1911
01:18:23,240 --> 01:18:24,500
"When Life Gives You Tangerines."

1912
01:18:25,440 --> 01:18:26,909
"When Life Gives You Tangerines."

1913
01:18:26,910 --> 01:18:29,240
- I see. - It's because he's from Jeju.

1914
01:18:29,810 --> 01:18:31,809
Hello, I'm from Jeju.

1915
01:18:30,980 --> 01:18:32,609
(Jeju Blue Ribbon Hoarder, Kim Si Yeob)

1916
01:18:31,810 --> 01:18:34,250
I'm Jeju Blue Ribbon Hoarder, Kim Si Yeob.

1917
01:18:32,610 --> 01:18:34,480
