2032
01:24:05,540 --> 01:24:06,680
This is really...

2033
01:24:08,110 --> 01:24:09,180
It's the real thing.

2034
01:24:10,850 --> 01:24:12,120
I think people would like it.

2035
01:24:14,690 --> 01:24:15,720
It's fragrant.

2036
01:24:16,590 --> 01:24:18,120
