2050
01:25:02,970 --> 01:25:06,710
Why did you use ripple jam today?

2051
01:25:05,270 --> 01:25:07,870
(Why did you use ripple jam today?)

2052
01:25:06,840 --> 01:25:09,040
Why did you use ripple jam today?

2053
01:25:10,580 --> 01:25:11,610
Moreover,

2054
