2055
01:25:16,680 --> 01:25:18,620
- Sorry? They don't go well? - No, they don't.

2056
01:25:18,880 --> 01:25:21,919
How could they? It's strawberry and roasted bean.

2057
01:25:21,920 --> 01:25:22,990
