2267
01:33:40,050 --> 01:33:42,350
It was the main product of our hotel,

2268
01:33:40,990 --> 01:33:45,990
(The hotel's main dish that was sold out often)

2269
01:33:42,490 --> 01:33:45,860
and it was sold out many times too.

2270
01:33:46,190 --> 01:33:48,589
The main chocolate that I used...

2271
01:33:48,590 --> 01:33:50,260
is called valrhona caraibe.

2272
01:33:49,660 --> 01:33:51,799
(Valrhona caraibe)

2273
01:33:50,460 --> 01:33:51,959
It has the tanginess of fruit...

2274
01:33:51,800 --> 01:33:55,770
